APIs for closing and re-opening a Solution.
Provided in ClearBasic and in JavaScript (using the Dovetail SDK via COM).

Includes 2 new activity codes: Close Solution and Reopen Solution
These should be imported into your database using dataex, diet, or UI Editor

Includes example code for form 321 (Solution form) for the Clarify Classic Client.
This shows how to use these APIs, including calling them from new buttons, as well as proper enabling of the form.

